  "id": "cli/test",
  "title": "ng test",
  "contents": "\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/edit/master/packages/angular/cli/commands/test.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/tree/v7.0.0-rc.3/packages/angular/cli/commands/test.json\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n  <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n    {\n      \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n      \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n      \"itemListElement\": [\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli\", \"name\": \"CLI\" } },\n        { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/cli/test\", \"name\": \"test\" } }\n      ]\n    }\n  </script>\n    <a href=\"cli\">CLI</a>\n</div>\n\n  \n<header class=\"cli-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"ng-test\">ng test<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"cli/test#ng-test\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n</header>\n\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"cli-body\">\n    \n    <p>Runs unit tests in a project.</p>\n\n    \n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">test</span> &#x3C;<var>project</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n<code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ng <span class=\"cli-name\">t</span> &#x3C;<var>project</var>> [<var>options</var>]</code-example>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"arguments\">Arguments</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Argument</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n  <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n    <td><code>&#x3C;<var>project</var>></code></td>\n    <td>\n      <p>The name of the project to build. Can be an app or a library.</p>\n\n      \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n\n<h2 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"options\">Options</h2>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Option</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--browsers=<var>browsers</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Override which browsers tests are run against.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--codeCoverage=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Output a code coverage report.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--codeCoverageExclude</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Globs to exclude from code coverage.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--configuration=<var>configuration</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>A named configuration environment, as specified in the \"configurations\" section of angular.json.</p>\n\n        \n        <p><span class=\"cli-aliases\">Aliases:</span> -c</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--environment=<var>environment</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Defines the build environment.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--evalSourceMap=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Output in-file eval sourcemaps.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--help=<br>    true|false|json|JSON</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Shows a help message for this command in the console.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--karmaConfig=<var>karmaConfig</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>The name of the Karma configuration file.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--main=<var>main</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>The name of the main entry-point file.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--poll</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Enable and define the file watching poll time period in milliseconds.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--polyfills=<var>polyfills</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>The name of the polyfills file.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--preserveSymlinks=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Do not use the real path when resolving modules.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--prod=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>When true, sets the build configuration to the production environment.\nAll builds make use of bundling and limited tree-shaking, A production build also runs limited dead code elimination using UglifyJS.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--progress=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Log progress to the console while building.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--reporters</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Karma reporters to use. Directly passed to the karma runner.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--sourceMap=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Output sourcemaps.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>true</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--tsConfig=<var>tsConfig</var></code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>The name of the TypeScript configuration file.</p>\n\n        \n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--vendorSourceMap=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Resolve vendor packages sourcemaps.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr class=\"cli-option\">\n      <td>\n        <code class=\"cli-option-syntax\">--watch=true|false</code>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>Run build when files change.</p>\n\n        <p><span class=\"cli-default\">Default:</span> <code>false</code></p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n    \n    \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/testing\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - cli/test#ng-test\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/edit/master/packages/angular/cli/commands/test.json?message=docs(...)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/tree/v7.0.0-rc.3/packages/angular/cli/commands/test.json\n-->"
